@startuml 07-deployment-aws
title Deployment Diagram - AWS (kien truc don gian, chi phi thap cho demo)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #E65100
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
}
skinparam queue {
  BackgroundColor #FCE4EC
}

actor "RM / Tham dinh vien /\nCompliance Officer / Credit Officer" as USER

cloud "Internet" as INTERNET

node "AWS Account - VPC (2 AZ)" {

  node "Public Subnet" {
    component "Application Load Balancer\n(internal-facing, qua VPN/Direct Connect\nhoac SSO qua Cognito)" as ALB
    component "NAT Gateway" as NAT
  }

  node "Private Subnet - Compute" {
    node "ECS Fargate Service\n\"adk-orchestrator-svc\"\n(chay `adk api_server`,\nauto-scaling 2-6 tasks)" as ADK_SVC
    node "ECS Fargate Service\n\"omnirouter-svc\"\n(self-hosted OpenAI-compatible\nrouter)" as ROUTER_SVC
  }

  node "Private Subnet - Data" {
    database "Aurora PostgreSQL\nServerless v2 + pgvector\n(RAG vector store)" as AURORA
    database "DynamoDB\n(ADK session/state store)" as DDB
  }

  component "S3: raw-documents" as S3_RAW
  component "S3: knowledge-corpus" as S3_KB
  component "S3: reports" as S3_REPORT

  queue "SQS: aml-review-queue" as SQS_AML
  queue "SQS: credit-approval-queue" as SQS_APPROVE
  component "SNS Notifications" as SNS

  component "Secrets Manager\n(DB creds, Omnirouter/LLM API keys)" as SECRETS
  component "CloudWatch + X-Ray\n(logs, agent trace dashboard)" as CW
  component "ECR (container images)" as ECR
}

cloud "Upstream LLM Provider(s)\n(OpenAI-compatible endpoint)" as LLM_UPSTREAM

USER --> ALB
ALB --> ADK_SVC
ADK_SVC --> ROUTER_SVC : internal call\n(Cloud Map / internal DNS)
ADK_SVC --> AURORA : RAG queries (pgvector)
ADK_SVC --> DDB : session state
ADK_SVC --> S3_RAW : doc ho so
ADK_SVC --> S3_KB : ingest RAG corpus
ADK_SVC --> S3_REPORT : ghi to trinh
ADK_SVC --> SQS_AML : enqueue task (HITL)
ADK_SVC --> SQS_APPROVE : enqueue task (HITL)
SQS_AML --> SNS
SQS_APPROVE --> SNS
SNS --> USER : email/Slack

ROUTER_SVC --> NAT
NAT --> INTERNET
INTERNET --> LLM_UPSTREAM

ADK_SVC ..> SECRETS : doc credentials
ROUTER_SVC ..> SECRETS : doc API key upstream
ADK_SVC ..> CW : logs/traces
ROUTER_SVC ..> CW : logs/traces

ECR --> ADK_SVC : pull image
ECR --> ROUTER_SVC : pull image

note bottom of ROUTER_SVC
  Gia dinh: Omnirouter (tu host) chi la lop routing/proxy,
  KHONG tu chua model weights -> can egress internet
  toi upstream LLM provider qua NAT Gateway.
  Neu Omnirouter cung tu host model (can GPU),
  can them EC2 (g5/p4d) hoac SageMaker endpoint
  trong private subnet - bao minh de cap nhat diagram.
end note

@enduml
